PN,43601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FSewage spilled into rivers, lakes and
OL,7,Fseas from storm overflows for longer
OL,8,Facross Devon and Cornwall in 2025 than
OL,9,Fany other part of the country,
OL,10,Faccording to new figures from the
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency.
OL,13,FThey show that excess water spilled
OL,14,Fthrough storm overflows for a total of
OL,15,F407,006 hours - the equivalent of
OL,16,F17,000 days.
OL,18,FThat figure puts South West Water as
OL,19,Fthe worst performing water company in
OL,20,FEngland for the length of time the
OL,21,Fspills lasted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
