OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FSouth West Water supplies water and
OL,7,Fwastewater services to 1.8 million
OL,8,Fcustomers across Cornwall, Devon, the
OL,9,FIsles of Scilly and parts of Dorset
OL,10,Fand Somerset.
OL,12,FThe total number of spills was just
OL,13,Fover 46,000, with South West Water as
OL,14,Fthe third worst performing company,
OL,15,Fbehind United Utilities and Yorkshire
OL,16,FWater.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FThe water company said the situation
OL,7,Fhadn't been helped by high rainfall,
OL,8,Fwith the South West experiencing 62
OL,9,Fper cent more rain than the rest of
OL,10,FEngland in 2025.
OL,12,FBosses also highlighted the company's
OL,13,Fsuccess at cutting storm overflow
OL,14,Fspills by 17 per cent and the duration
OL,15,Fof spills by 25 per cent.
OL,17,FEnvironmental campaigners dismissed
OL,18,Fthese points, claiming that it was
OL,19,Funfair to blame the weather, as the
OL,20,FSouth West always experiences high
OL,21,Frainfall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FJo Bateman from Exmouth , who has
OL,7,Fbrought a case against South West
OL,8,FWater for discharging sewage into the
OL,9,Fsea, said: "South West Water cannot
OL,10,Fuse the weather as any kind of excuse,
OL,11,Fbecause it is always wet here. It is
OL,12,Fnot exceptional. The situation is not
OL,13,Fgetting any better.
OL,15,F"They are the worst company with the
OL,16,Ftotal duration of monitored spills."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FShe added: "It is a human right to
OL,7,Fhave clean water. It does not make any
OL,8,Fsense to have a privatised system
OL,9,Fwhich is a monopoly where people have
OL,10,Fno choice about who supplies them with
OL,11,Fwater.
OL,13,F"I, along with many other people,
OL,14,Fwould not mind paying more to know the
OL,15,Finfrastructure was being improved."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FAsked if the imminent arrival of a new
OL,7,FCEO would make any difference, she
OL,8,Fadded: "As a CEO their prime goal is
OL,9,Fto make money for shareholders. I
OL,10,Fcannot see that the arrival of a new
OL,11,FCEO will make any difference, but I
OL,12,Flive in hope."
OL,14,FA statement from South West Water said
OL,15,Fprogress was being made to reduce the
OL,16,Fnumber of spills and the duration.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,FIt said: "The South West saw 62% more
OL,7,Frain than the rest of England in 2025.
OL,8,FDespite this, we still cut storm
OL,9,Foverflow spills by 17% and spill
OL,10,Fduration by 25%.
OL,12,F"We also prevented more than 8,300
OL,13,Fspills, due to operational
OL,14,Fimprovement, with a focus on beaches
OL,15,Fduring bathing season - a clear sign
OL,16,Four #760 million investment plan is
OL,17,Falready producing strong results.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774555873
OL,3,CLength of storm overflow spills longer
OL,4,Cin South West than rest of England
OL,6,F"There's more to do, but the direction
OL,7,Fis clear: fewer spills, shorter
OL,8,Fdurations, and investment where it
OL,9,Fmatters most."
OL,11,FSewage spilled into England's rivers,
OL,12,Flakes and seas from storm overflows
OL,13,Ffor more than 1.87 million hours in
OL,14,F2025 even as drier weather cut
OL,15,Fpollution, according to the national
OL,16,Ffigures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
